  "short_description": "Total Arcade Racing is a fun 2D top-down arcade racing game where you zip around closed circuits. Play solo or with up to 8 friends on the same screen in various game modes.​ This game is a tribute to old school arcade racing games like Super Sprint, Slicks 'n' Slide and Super Cars.",
