  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264730/extras/72f94d2cbdfa80292926914320d24096.poster.avif?t=1773168778\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264730/extras/72f94d2cbdfa80292926914320d24096.webm?t=1773168778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264730/extras/72f94d2cbdfa80292926914320d24096.mp4?t=1773168778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience fast-paced arcade racing action in Total Arcade Racing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race solo or with up to 8 players on the same screen across multiple game modes. Inspired by classic top-down racers like Super Sprint, Slicks ’n Slide and Super cars. Total Arcade Racing features tight controls, thrilling tracks, and non-stop fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge players from around the world in the global leaderboard. Can you claim the #1 spot in the Hall of Fame? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 Cars</strong> – Each with unique speed and handling</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>16 Tracks</strong> – Fast, fun, and full of twists</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>9 game modes -</strong> (Arcade Race, Time trial, Championship, Elimination, Endless race, Demolition derby, Survivor, Delivery and Car Hockey)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8-Player Local Multiplayer</strong> – Couch chaos at its best</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Remote Play Together</strong> <strong>-</strong> support for 8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Global Leaderboards</strong> – Race for world domination</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ghost Replays</strong> – Beat the fastest drivers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tight Controls</strong> – Classic top-down racing controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Party ready game – </strong>Race against your friends and family</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controller & Keyboard Support</strong> – Play your way</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264730/extras/a872d496f340b2a9d3b35f4ff7108e45.poster.avif?t=1773168778\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264730/extras/a872d496f340b2a9d3b35f4ff7108e45.webm?t=1773168778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264730/extras/a872d496f340b2a9d3b35f4ff7108e45.mp4?t=1773168778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264730/extras/72f94d2cbdfa80292926914320d24096.poster.avif?t=1773168778\" width=616 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264730/extras/72f94d2cbdfa80292926914320d24096.webm?t=1773168778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264730/extras/72f94d2cbdfa80292926914320d24096.mp4?t=1773168778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience fast-paced arcade racing action in Total Arcade Racing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race solo or with up to 8 players on the same screen across multiple game modes. Inspired by classic top-down racers like Super Sprint, Slicks ’n Slide and Super cars. Total Arcade Racing features tight controls, thrilling tracks, and non-stop fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge players from around the world in the global leaderboard. Can you claim the #1 spot in the Hall of Fame? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>7 Cars</strong> – Each with unique speed and handling</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>16 Tracks</strong> – Fast, fun, and full of twists</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>9 game modes -</strong> (Arcade Race, Time trial, Championship, Elimination, Endless race, Demolition derby, Survivor, Delivery and Car Hockey)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8-Player Local Multiplayer</strong> – Couch chaos at its best</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Remote Play Together</strong> <strong>-</strong> support for 8 players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Global Leaderboards</strong> – Race for world domination</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ghost Replays</strong> – Beat the fastest drivers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tight Controls</strong> – Classic top-down racing controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Party ready game – </strong>Race against your friends and family</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controller & Keyboard Support</strong> – Play your way</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264730/extras/a872d496f340b2a9d3b35f4ff7108e45.poster.avif?t=1773168778\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264730/extras/a872d496f340b2a9d3b35f4ff7108e45.webm?t=1773168778\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1264730/extras/a872d496f340b2a9d3b35f4ff7108e45.mp4?t=1773168778\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
